description: Transport yourself to the sun-soaked streets of 1950s and 1960s Italy with this handpicked playlist of timeless classics. From the enchanting melodies of Gino Paoli to the soulful serenades of Mina, "La Dolce Estate" will sweep you away to a bygone era of romantic Mediterranean summers.
name: La Dolce Estate: Vintage Italian Summer Vibes
